<HEADLINE> Cohen Arrives in Ankara for Visit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 14 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Secretary of Defense William
Cohen arrived here Wednesday evening after visiting U.S. Incirlik
Air Base in Adana, southern Turkey.
</P>
<P>
Cohen toured the Incirlik Air Base, home of British and
American air forces that patrol the no-fly zone in northern Iraq.
</P>
<P>
U.S. warplanes Wednesday bombarded military facilities in
northern Iraq before Cohen's special plane landed at the air
base.
</P>
<P>
During the Gulf War in 1991, the U.S. used the base to attack
military targets in northern Iraq.
</P>
