University and streets nearby, condemning the unrest in the past
week triggered by student protests against police crackdown on
student hostels.
</P>
<P>
The conservative Majlis (parliament) Speaker Ali Akbar Nateq-
Nouri along with a number of cabinet ministers and Majlis
deputies took part in the grand rally.
(BC-Iran-Rallies-Conservatives)
</P>
<P>
