globalized market with their own cultural and ideological
identity.
</P>
<P>
On the issue of debt relief, he said, it was good but the more
fundamental solution was increasing African production and export
capacity.
</P>
<P>
Museveni cautioned African leaders against proposing solutions
to armed conflicts on the continent without first analysing the
cause. 
