in the city. On June 5, a Japanese foreign aid expert had three
fingers bitten by a shark while surfing. He managed to escape and
took a chartered flight to South Africa for a surgery.
</P>
<P>
The Tanzanian authorities have warned people especially
students not to venture out in some sea areas. 
