<HEADLINE> Forest Protection Festival In Central China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 15 (Xinhua) -- The '99 China Ecological Tour
Hunan Zhangjiajie International Forest Protection Festival will be
held from September 22 to 27 in Zhangjiajie City in Hunan Province.
</P>
<P>
The festival's theme is " Man and Nature, Fusion of Nature with
Culture". It is sponsored by the National Tourism Administration,
State Environmental Protection Administration, Chinese Academy of
Sciences and Hunan Provincial Government.
</P>
<P>
