during the festival, and he said the city can provide
accommodation for them.
</P>
<P>
Zhangjiajie, in northwestern Hunan has a population of 1.54
million, 72 percent of them members of ethnic groups.
</P>
<P>
In 1982, Zhangjiajie was approved by the State Council as the
first state forest park in China, and was listed as one of the
World Heritage by UNESCO in 1992. 
