market and also help the United States to get access to the
Vietnamese market, as well as create favorable conditions for U.S.
businessmen to do business and investment in Vietnam.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam and the United State have conducted eight rounds of
trade negotiations since September 1996.
</P>
<P>
Thanks to joint efforts by both sides, Thanh said, Vietnam and
the United States narrowed the outstanding issues in the latest
round of trade negotiations from June 14 to June 18, 1999.
</P>
<P>
Both Vietnam and the United States are continuing to make
efforts to solve outstanding issues for a trade agreement as soon
as possible, said Thanh. 
