<HEADLINE> "One China" Principle, Basis for Cross-straits Relationship </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 15 (Xinhua) -- "One China" principle is the basis
for cross-Straits relations and cooperation between the
Association for Relations Across the Taiwan Straits (ARATS) and
the Straits Exchange Foundation (SEF), Chinese Foreign Ministry
spokeswoman said today.
</P>
