O Than jetty of the port, it said.
</P>
<P>
The fire spread rapidly to other three vessels which were
anchored nearby.
</P>
<P>
The fire lasted for more than an hour before it died out at
7:45 a.m. (local Time).
</P>
<P>
The cause of the fire is under investigation. 
