year, an official press release available Thursday said.
</P>
<P>
The activities include the Royal Barge Procession, cultural
shows, the Lion Dance Contest, the International Dance Contest,
the Traditional Sports Festival, light and sound shows and others,
the Government Public Relations Department quoted the Bangkok
Metropolitan Administration (BMA) as saying.
</P>
