Treaty on Friendly Cooperative Relations five years ago in view of
the new development, in which the two sides reiterate their stance
to further promote goodneighborly and friendly relations of
cooperation on the basis of mutual respect for independence,
sovereignty and territorial integrity, non-mutual interference in
each other's internal affairs, equality, mutual benefit and
peaceful co-existence.
