<HEADLINE> Chinese President Speaks about Sino-Mongolian Ties (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The two countries are complementary to each other in the
economy and trade, Jiang said, explaining that Mongolia has rich
natural resources, including copper, iron, coal and oil, while
China has technologies and products that are suited to Mongolia.
</P>
<P>
"China and Mongolia should give full play to these advantages,
and conduct economic and trade cooperation based on equality and
