-- Premier Zhu Rongji visited Hubei and Jiangxi provinces on
Monday and Tuesday to make arrangements for the fight against
possible summer floods.
</P>
<P>
At a meeting in Wuhan, Zhu asked all local governments of areas
along the Yangtze River to do their best to prepare for the fight
and ensure the quality of flood-control projects in order to
guarantee the safety of the lives and properties of millions of
people.
</P>
