<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Indian Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, July 15 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Indian newspapers Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The Hindustan Times:
</P>
<P>
-- India Wednesday warned that any intruder continuing to
